'''高貴紅菇'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Russula nobilis'''''}}）<ref name=Phillips06>{{cite book | author = Roger Phillips. | year = 2006  | title = Mushrooms| publisher = Pan MacMillan | isbn = 0-330-44237-6|page=19}}</ref>，俗稱'''山毛櫸病患'''（{{lang|en|beechwood sickener}}），是一種[[擔子菌門|擔子菌門]][[真菌|真菌]]，隸屬於俗稱脆褶（''{{lang|en|Brittlegill}}''）的[[紅菇屬|紅菇屬]]。<ref>"Danske storsvampe.  Basidiesvampe" [a key to Danish basidiomycetes] J.H. Petersen and J. Vesterholt eds. Gyldendal. Viborg, Denmark, 1990.  ISBN 87-01-09932-9</ref>這種真菌體形適中，顏色為紅色或玫瑰色，且是不可供食用的。<ref name="Roger"/>

==分類==
對高貴紅菇最早的描述者是1920年的捷克真菌學家{{link-en|約瑟夫·維倫諾夫斯基|Josef Velenovský}}，其學名即為現今的學名。而其[[異名|異名]]「美丽紅菇」（{{lang|la|''Russula mairei''}}）則是由德國真菌學家[[羅爾夫·辛格|羅爾夫·辛格]]於1929年給予的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mycobank.org/Biolomics.aspx?Table=Mycobank&MycoBankNr_=270363 |title=Russula mairei - MycoBank |accessdate=2013-11-23 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202223514/http://www.mycobank.org/Biolomics.aspx?Table=Mycobank&MycoBankNr_=270363 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其[[植物學名命名法|學名]]中的「''{{lang|la|nobilis}}''」源自[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]，意思是「高貴的」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mycobank.org/Biolomics.aspx?Table=Mycobank&MycoBankNr_=272416 |title=Russula nobilis - MycoBank |accessdate=2013-11-23 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202221408/http://www.mycobank.org/Biolomics.aspx?Table=Mycobank&MycoBankNr_=272416 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==描述==
高貴紅菇的[[菌蓋|菌蓋]]直徑約為3–6厘米（1.2–2.4英寸），呈紅色、玫瑰色或白色，且稍具粘性。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wildfooduk.com/mushroom-guides/beechwood-sickener-mushroom/ |title=Beechwood Sickener, Russula mairei - Wild Food UK |access-date=2013-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814121847/http://www.wildfooduk.com/mushroom-guides/beechwood-sickener-mushroom |archive-date=2018-08-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>起初呈凸面狀，但隨著年齡增加會漸漸變成扁平狀或下陷狀。<ref name=Phillips06/>其[[菌柄|菌柄]]高2.5–4.5厘米，厚1–1.5厘米，穩固，呈白色，形狀為圓柱形。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mycorance.free.fr/valchamp/champi415.htm |title=russule noble, russula nobilis |accessdate=2013-11-23 |archive-date=2012-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426195544/http://mycorance.free.fr/valchamp/champi415.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>其[[菌褶|菌褶]]是自由下垂的，呈白色，有時候會染有藍綠色的色調，且它們之間的間距不大。菌蓋部份的[[菌肉|菌肉]]呈粉紅色，而菌柄部份的菌肉則呈白色。其味道辛辣，且年輕時有著類似椰子的氣味。其[[孢子印|孢子印]]呈白色，而橢圓形[[擔孢子|擔孢子]]的大小則為7–8 x 6–6.5微米。<ref name="Roger">[http://www.rogersmushrooms.com/gallery/DisplayBlock~bid~6030~gid~~source~gallerydefault.asp Rogers Mushrooms - Russula mairei Mushroom] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203163417/http://www.rogersmushrooms.com/gallery/DisplayBlock~bid~6030~gid~~source~gallerydefault.asp |date=2013-12-03 }}</ref>

==分佈及生境==
高貴紅菇廣泛地分佈於[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[北美洲|北美洲]]和[[歐洲|歐洲]]，並且通常於秋季在林地區域中出現。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.first-nature.com/fungi/russula-nobilis.php |title=Russula nobilis, Beechwood Sickener mushroom - First Nature |accessdate=2013-11-23 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203112508/http://www.first-nature.com/fungi/russula-nobilis.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>這種真菌是以[[菌根|外生菌根]]的方式依附著[[水青冈属|山毛櫸]]生長。<ref name=T.Laessoe>{{cite book | author = Thomas Laessoe. | year = 1998 | title = Mushrooms (flexi bound) | publisher = Dorling Kindersley | isbn = 0-7513-1070-0}}</ref>

==可食性==
高貴紅菇有著辛辣的味道，且可能含有有毒成份，因此是不可供食用的。很多類似的紅菇屬真菌在生吃時也是是有毒的。進食有毒紅菇屬真菌在後的症狀主要是與胃腸道有關的：[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、嘔吐和腹部絞痛。<ref>Andina D. ''et al''. (1980). Sesquiterpenes from ''Russula sardonia''. ''Phytochemistry'' '''19''': 93–97</ref>雖然高貴紅菇的有毒成份仍然未知，但真菌學家們指出有毒成份很可能是有毒紅菇獨有的[[倍半萜|倍半萜]]。<ref>{{cite book |last=Benjamin| first= Denis R. |title=Mushrooms: poisons and panaceas — a handbook for naturalists, mycologists and physicians|url=https://archive.org/details/mushroomspoisons0000benj|page= [https://archive.org/details/mushroomspoisons0000benj/page/369 369]|publisher=WH Freeman and Company| location=New York |year=1995| isbn=0-7167-2600-9}}</ref>

